## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. When we do, we’ll revise the date at the top of this page and, if significant, notify you directly.

## Final Notes

- Your trust is important. We are committed to transparency and safeguarding your privacy.
- You have control over your data and can manage your preferences or request removal at any time.
- For further questions or assistance, don’t hesitate to reach out to us.

Thank you for being a part of the Cats Hub community, where we share expert insights to help you and your feline friends thrive!
